<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vijayābhyuda<unclear>ya</unclear> śālivāhana śakava<unclear>rṣa</unclear>
<lb n="2"/><unclear>14</unclear>31 saṁda śu<unclear>kla</unclear>saṁvatsarada bhādrapada śu 1 lū śrīmaN ma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>hārājādhirāja rājaparamēśvara pūrvadakṣiṇapa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ścimasamudrādhīśvara mēdinīmosaragaṁḍa kaṭhāri
<lb n="5" break="no"/>sāḷuva vīrabhujabalarāya mahārāyara bhujapratāparā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>da tipparasayana kāryyakke karttarāda <unclear>si</unclear>riyappayyanavaru
<lb n="7"/>śrī <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ṁgaṁḍa tiṁmarāya cakravarti Ayyanava
<lb n="8" break="no"/><unclear>ru</unclear> koṭṭa dharmmasādhanada krama muḷuvāgila cāvaḍiya ḍeṁkaṇe
<lb n="9" break="no"/>kōṭeya nāyakatanakke salluva maṁjināḍa peṁṇṇagarada sī
<lb n="10" break="no"/>meya kūtapāḍiya grāmava sarvamānya<unclear>yēkabhōgya</unclear>vāgi sūryya
<lb n="11" break="no"/>grahaṇapuṁṇyakāladalli sahiraṇyōdakadhārāpūrvvakavāgi timma
